---
/**
 * 变体 V1：Linear / Anthropic 风
 * ---
 * DNA:
 *  - 象牙白底 #F5F7FA + 科技蓝 #0078D8 单点缀
 *  - Cormorant 衬线大标题 + Inter 正文
 *  - 无 emoji · 无渐变 · 无粒子
 *  - 学术气质、克制、纯排版驱动
 *  - 唯一"动"的元素：SVG Logo 呼吸微光斑（静态 CSS）
 *
 * Trace 到 brand-spec.md:
 *  §2.2 主色 · §3 字体 · §5 无 GPU 粒子 · §6 参照 Linear/Anthropic
 */
---
<html lang="zh-CN" data-variant="v1-linear">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>V1 · Linear/Anthropic 风 - 光电科技</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #F5F7FA;
        --surface: #FFFFFF;
        --brand: #0078D8;
        --brand-hover: #0088F0;
        --brand-deep: #1878C0;
        --tint: #D8F0F0;
        --text: #1a2332;
        --text-muted: #6090A8;
        --border: rgba(0,120,216,0.12);
      }
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans SC', system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      /* 顶部导航 - 极简 */
      header {
        position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
        background: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      nav {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .brand {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
        text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
      }
      .brand img {
        width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,120,216,0.15);
      }
      .brand-name {
        font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .brand-en {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted);
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }
      nav ul {
        display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; list-style: none; align-items: center;
      }
      nav a {
        text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      nav a:hover { color: var(--brand); }
      .cta {
        background: var(--brand); color: white !important;
        border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.5rem 1rem !important;
      }
      .cta:hover { background: var(--brand-hover); color: white !important; }

      /* Hero - 排版驱动 */
      .hero {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 8rem 1.5rem 6rem;
        position: relative;
      }
      /* CSS 静态光晕 - 唯一"动"的元素 */
      .glow {
        position: absolute; pointer-events: none;
        width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(120px); opacity: 0.4;
      }
      .glow-1 { top: -100px; right: 10%; background: #0078D8; }
      .glow-2 { bottom: 0; left: 5%; background: #A8D8D8; opacity: 0.3; }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--brand-deep);
        background: rgba(0,120,216,0.08);
        padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 999px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .eyebrow-dot {
        width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--brand); animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      }
      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; }
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        max-width: 800px;
      }
      h1 em {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--brand);
      }
      .sub {
        font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .btn-primary {
        background: var(--brand); color: white;
        padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background: var(--brand-hover);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,120,216,0.25);
      }
      .btn-secondary {
        background: transparent; color: var(--text);
        padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--brand); color: var(--brand); }

      /* 数据展示 - 单行排列 · 无卡片 */
      .stats {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 3rem;
      }
      .stat-item {
        text-align: left;
      }
      .stat-num {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--brand); line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .stat-label {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
      }

      /* 方向 - 学术排版 */
      .directions {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 8rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .section-desc {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }
      .dir-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 3rem;
      }
      .dir-item h3 {
        font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .dir-item h3::before {
        content: ''; display: inline-block;
        width: 32px; height: 2px;
        background: var(--brand);
        margin-right: 0.75rem; vertical-align: middle;
      }
      .dir-item p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      /* 精神 - 无卡片 · 大字排版 */
      .spirit {
        background: var(--surface);
        padding: 8rem 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .spirit-content {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .spirit-word {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      .spirit-word em {
        color: var(--brand);
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .spirit-sub {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 0 auto;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
      }
      footer h4 {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      footer p, footer li {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.75;
      }
      footer ul { list-style: none; }
      footer a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      footer a:hover { color: var(--brand); }
      .copyright {
        max-width: 1152px; margin: 3rem auto 0;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        nav ul { gap: 0; }
        nav a { padding: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <img src="/logo.jpg" alt="光电科技 Logo" />
          <div>
            <div class="brand-name">光电科技</div>
            <div class="brand-en">Photoelectric Technology</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/team">团队</a></li>
          <li><a href="/projects">项目</a></li>
          <li><a href="/devices">设备</a></li>
          <li><a href="/items">资产</a></li>
          <li><a href="/recruit" class="cta">加入我们</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="glow glow-1"></div>
      <div class="glow glow-2"></div>

      <div class="eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
        EST. 2016 · 河南理工大学物理与电子信息学院
      </div>

      <h1>
        我们用<em>光</em>与<em>电</em><br />
        编写未来的可能
      </h1>

      <p class="sub">
        大学生光电科技协会，扎根河南理工大学物理与电子信息学院。<br />
        崇尚创新、学习、交流、竞技四大精神，在硬件与代码的交汇处，孕育下一代工程师。
      </p>

      <div class="buttons">
        <a href="/recruit" class="btn-primary">加入我们 →</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn-secondary">查看项目</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">80+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">活跃成员</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">175</div>
        <div class="stat-label">国家级奖项</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">182</div>
        <div class="stat-label">省级奖项</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">2016</div>
        <div class="stat-label">创立年份</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="directions">
      <h2 class="section-title">研究方向</h2>
      <div class="section-desc">RESEARCH — 03 fields</div>
      <div class="dir-grid">
        <div class="dir-item">
          <h3>光电技术</h3>
          <p>激光通信、光纤传感、LED 驱动、光学测量——把光当成数据的载体，探索信息与能量在光子层面的耦合。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dir-item">
          <h3>嵌入式开发</h3>
          <p>单片机、FPGA、树莓派、ESP32——用代码让硬件听话，在电路与逻辑的边界重构物理世界的反馈闭环。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dir-item">
          <h3>创客实践</h3>
          <p>3D 打印、激光雕刻、PCB 设计——从构思到实物的完整路径，让协会实验室成为想法孕育的产房。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="spirit">
      <div class="spirit-content">
        <div class="spirit-word">
          追随<em>光</em>&emsp;靠近<em>光</em><br />
          成为<em>光</em>&emsp;发散<em>光</em>
        </div>
        <div class="spirit-sub">— 协会信条 · SINCE 2016 —</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div>
        <h4>光电科技 · Photoelectric Technology</h4>
        <p>河南理工大学大学生光电科技协会。<br />依托物理与电子信息学院，致力于光电技术、嵌入式开发、创客实践与科技竞赛。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>内部资源</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">飞书知识库 →</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">NAS 共享盘 →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>联系我们</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>QQ 群：待填写</li>
          <li>邮箱：待填写</li>
          <li>河南理工大学 北校区</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <div class="copyright">
      © 2016—2026 光电科技 · Photoelectric Technology · 河南理工大学物理与电子信息学院
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
